Azure student email troubleshooting instructions

1. Visit https://github.com/login
2. Log in using your GIthub userID and not email address.
3. Click on your profile in the upper right hand corner then click on "Settings"
4. Make sure same email address that you used to sign up is listed under "Emails" and that it is chosen as the â€œPrimary email
5. Then go to - https://signup.azure.com/studentverification?offerType=1.
6. Click on "Sign in with your Github" 
7. If you get stuck in the verification page, kindly show the options you see available.
8. Choose Github option. If you get an error message that your student status is not verified, please click on "here.

